TriggerLogic.Name: GUI Message
TriggerLogic.Message: Our commander was captured and is held by the enemy deep inside a mountainous forest. The ground defence is likely to be too strong and we'll need to air-lift the commander out, but first we'll have to remove the enemy anti-air towers and bring down their fighter shield. Intelligence suggests the enemy aircraft plants are located in the north-east. We must work fast since enemy reinforcements will arrive in 20 minutes.

TriggerLogic.Name: Marker
TriggerLogic.Text: Fly the commander here to complete the mission.
